<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta
            name="viewport"
            content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
        >
        <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
        <script
            defer
            src="https://unpkg.com/alpinejs"
        ></script>
        <style>
            [x-cloak] {
                display: none !important;
            }
        </style>
        <title>Document</title>
    </head>

    <body>
        <!-- \ x-transition -->
        <div x-data="{ open: false }">
            <button x-on:click="open = ! open">transition btn</button>

            <div
                x-show="open"
                x-transition:enter.duration.200ms
                x-transition:leave.duration.2000ms
            >
                Content
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div
            class="space-y-4 p-4"
            x-data="{open:true}"
        >
            <button
                class="bg-slate-500 px-4 py-2 text-white"
                @click="open=!open"
            >toggle</button>
            <div
                class="p-4 border border-bg-slate-500"
                x-show="open"
                x-transition:enter="transition duration-500 ease-out"
                x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 scale-50"
                x-transition:leave="transition duration-500 ease-in"
                x-transition:leave-end="opacity-100 scale-50"
            >Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nisi laudantium ducimus nemo, assumenda placeat
                in, sapiente dolorem nihil officiis voluptatum delectus ipsam temporibus molestiae, obcaecati rem.
                Cumque expedita tempora commodi.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-sm">
            <!-- Aufgabe: Durch shift + s die Sidebar ein- und ausblenden -->
            <div
                x-data="{ sidebar: false }"
                @keydown.shift.s.window="sidebar = !sidebar"
            >
                <div
                    class="left-0 fixed inset-y-0 bg-slate-500 w-80"
                    x-cloak
                    x-show="sidebar"
                    x-transition:enter="transition-all ease-out duration-500"
                    x-transition:enter-start="-left-80"
                    x-transition:enter-end="left-0"
                    x-transition:leave="transition-all ease-in duration-500"
                    x-transition:leave-start="left-0"
                    x-transition:leave-end="-left-80"
                >
                    <div class="flex flex-col divide-y text-slate-100">
                        <button class="hover:bg-slate-600 p-4">Button</button>
                        <button class="hover:bg-slate-600 p-4">Button</button>
                        <button class="hover:bg-slate-600 p-4">Button</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div class="flex lg:flex-row flex-col lg:gap-16">
            <div
                id="left"
                class="lg:w-1/2"
            >
                <div
                    id="new"
                    class="bg-gray-200 shadow p-2 rounded text-lg"
                >
                    <ul class="m-0">
                        <li class="mb-0">Adjust scaling, opacity, duration, delay and scaling direction with inline
                            modifiers together with <b>x-show</b>.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Example 1: (Orange) Pure use transition alone -->
                <h3 class="mt-8 mb-1 text-base">Example 1: x-transition alone</h3>
                <section
                    style="height:140px;"
                    class="flex mt-0"
                    x-data="{ visible: true }"
                >
                    <div>
                        <button
                            @click="visible = !visible"
                            class="bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 mr-8 mb-2 px-2 py-1 rounded h-8 focus:outline-none"
                        >Toggle visibility</button>
                        <div
                            x-show="visible"
                            x-transition
                            class="bg-yellow-500 w-24 h-24"
                        ></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-sm">Use only <b>x-transition</b> standalone</div>
                </section>

                <!-- Example2: (blue) Time modifier with "duration" and milliseconds-->
                <h3 class="mt-8 mb-1 text-base">Example 2: Duration</h3>
                <section
                    style="height:140px;"
                    class="flex h-24"
                    x-data="{ visible: true }"
                >
                    <div>
                        <button
                            @click="visible = !visible"
                            class="bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 mr-8 mb-2 px-2 py-1 rounded h-8 focus:outline-none"
                        >Toggle visibility</button>
                        <div
                            x-show="visible"
                            x-transition.duration.5000ms
                            class="bg-blue-500 w-24 h-24"
                        ></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-sm">Use <b>x-transition.duration.5000ms</b>.<br>Observe how the fading-in
                        is much faster than fading-out.<br>Time of the recording the fade-in is in 2500ms and the
                        fade-out in 5000ms.<br>Should be the other way around.<br>Wrote to Caleb about
                        this.<br>Maybe the time you see this lecture, it will be correct.</div>
                </section>

                <!-- Example 3: (green) Time modifier with dedicated enter and leave time -->
                <h3 class="mt-8 mb-1 text-base">Example 3: Specific Durations for "in" and "out"</h3>
                <section
                    style="height:140px;"
                    class="flex h-24"
                    x-data="{ visible: true }"
                >
                    <div>
                        <button
                            @click="visible = !visible"
                            class="bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 mr-8 mb-2 px-2 py-1 rounded h-8 focus:outline-none"
                        >Toggle visibility</button>
                        <div
                            x-show="visible"
                            x-transition:enter.duration.600ms
                            x-transition:leave.duration.300ms
                            class="bg-green-500 w-24 h-24"
                        ></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-sm">
                        <b>x-transition:enter.duration.600ms</b><br>
                        <b>x-transition:leave.duration.300ms</b><br>
                        Play around until it feels good.
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
            <div
                id="right"
                class="mt-10 lg:mt-0 lg:w-1/2"
            >

                <!-- Example 4 : Delay before fading out -->
                <h3 class="mt-8 mb-1 text-base">Example 4: Delay</h3>
                <section
                    class="flex h-32"
                    x-data="{ visible: false }"
                >
                    <div>
                        <button
                            @mouseenter="visible = true"
                            @mouseleave="visible = false"
                            class="bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 mr-8 px-2 py-1 rounded h-8 focus:outline-none"
                        >Show Menu</button>
                        <div
                            x-show="visible"
                            x-transition:enter.duration.500ms
                            x-transition:leave.duration.200ms.delay.3000ms
                            class="bg-blue-200 p-1 w-24 h-16"
                        >This is a submenu</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-sm">
                        On the button:<br>
                        @mouseenter="visible = true"<br>
                        @mouseleave="visible = false"<br>
                        On the "Menu":<br>
                        x-transition:enter.duration.500ms<br>
                        x-transition:leave.duration.200ms<b>.delay.3000ms</b><br>
                        >> User has 3 seconds time to do something with the submenu</div>
                </section>

                <!-- Example 5: (gray) Exclusive Opacity & Scale -->
                <h3 class="mt-8 mb-1 text-base">Example 5: Exclusive Opacity & Scale</h3>
                <section
                    style="height:140px;"
                    class="flex h-24"
                    x-data="{ visible: true }"
                >
                    <div>
                        <button
                            @click="visible = !visible"
                            class="bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 mr-8 mb-2 px-2 py-1 rounded h-8 focus:outline-none"
                        >Toggle visibility</button>
                        <div
                            x-show="visible"
                            x-transition:enter.duration.1000ms.scale.0
                            x-transition:leave.duration.600ms.scale.0
                            class="bg-gray-400 w-24 h-24"
                        ></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-sm">
                        Switch off scaling with opacity modifier:<br>
                        <b>x-transition:enter.duration.1000ms.opacity</b><br>
                        <b>x-transition:leave.duration.1000ms.opacity</b><br><br>
                        Switch off opacity with scale modifier: (only makes sense with scale = 0)<br>
                        <b>x-transition:enter.duration.1000ms.scale.0</b><br>
                        <b>x-transition:leave.duration.600ms.scale.0</b>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Example 6: Sliding from certain sides -->
                <h3 class="mt-8 mb-1 text-base">Example 6: Scaling in from certain sides</h3>
                <section
                    style="height:140px;"
                    class="flex h-24"
                    x-data="{ visible: true }"
                >
                    <div>
                        <button
                            @click="visible = !visible"
                            class="bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 mr-8 mb-2 px-2 py-1 rounded h-8 focus:outline-none"
                        >Toggle visibility</button>
                        <div
                            x-show="visible"
                            x-transition:enter.scale.0.origin.top.duration.1000ms
                            class="bg-red-400 w-24 h-24"
                        ></div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm">
                    Examples:<br>
                    x-transition:enter.scale.0.<b>origin.left.</b>duration.1000ms<br>
                    x-transition:enter.scale.0.<b>origin.top.right.</b>duration.1000ms<br>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <section
            x-data="{isOpen : false}"
            class="relative mt-8"
        >
            <!-- Round Button -->
            <button
                class="bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-800 shadow ml-44 p-4 rounded-full w-12 h-12 text-center text-gray-700 hover:text-white focus:outline-none transform transition duration-200"
                @click="isOpen = !isOpen"
                @click.away="isOpen = false"
                :class="{'rotate-45':isOpen}"
            >
                <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    class="w-8 h-8"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6"
                    />
                </svg>
            </button>

            <!-- The Menu that we animate with transitions -->
            <div
                class="absolute bg-white shadow-2xl border rounded-lg w-44"
                x-show="isOpen"
                x-transition:enter="transition ease-in-out duration-1000"
                x-transition:enter-start="transform origin-top scale-y-0 opacity-50 shadow-none"
                x-transition:enter-end="transform origin-top scale-y-100 opacity-100 shadow-2xl"
                x-transition:leave="transition ease-in-out duration-200"
                x-transition:leave-start="transform origin-top scale-y-100 opacity-100 shadow-2xl"
                x-transition:leave-end="transform origin-top scale-y-0 opacity-50 shadow-none"
            >
                <ul
                    id="example"
                    class="divide-y text-md"
                >
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="#"
                            class="block hover:bg-yellow-100 p-3"
                        >More information</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="#"
                            class="block hover:bg-yellow-100 p-3"
                        >Contact</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="#"
                            class="block hover:bg-yellow-100 p-3"
                        >Imprint</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section
            x-data="{isOpen : false}"
            class="relative mt-8"
        >
            <div
                @click="isOpen = !isOpen"
                @click.away="isOpen = false"
                id="button"
                class="inline-block bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300 px-2 py-1 cursor-pointer"
            >Open Menu</div>
            <!-- Submenu -->
            <div
                x-show="isOpen"
                x-cloak
                x-transition:enter="transition duration-4000"
                x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0"
                x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100"
                x-transition:leave="transition duration-1000"
                x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100"
                x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0"
                class="z-10 absolute mt-2"
                id="submenu"
            >
                <a
                    target="_blank"
                    class="inline-block bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300 px-2 py-1 w-32 cursor-pointer"
                    href="https://www.google.com"
                >Google</a><br>
                <a
                    target="_blank"
                    class="inline-block bg-blue-200 hover:bg-blue-300 px-2 py-1 w-32 cursor-pointer"
                    href="https://www.amazon.com"
                >Amazon</a><br>
            </div>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <section
            class="p-4"
            x-data="{ visible: false }"
        >
            <button
                class="border-2 border-violet-400"
                @click="visible = ! visible"
            > single transition</button>
            <div
                x-cloak
                x-show="visible"
                x-transition.duration.500ms.delay.200ms.opacity.20.scale.80.scale.origin.top.right
            >this message will animated from right</div>
        </section>
        <section
            class="p-4"
            x-data="{visible:false}"
        >
            <button
                class="border-2 border-yellow-700"
                @click="visible = ! visible"
            >multiple transition</button>
            <div
                x-cloak
                x-show="visible"
                x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300"
                x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 scale-90"
                x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 scale-100"
                x-transition:leave="transition ease-in duration-300"
                x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100 scale-100"
                x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0 scale-90"
            >this text has multiple transition</div>
        </section>
        <br>
        <hr>
        <div
            x-data="{'a': false}"
            class="m-20"
        >
            <button
                class="bg-red-300"
                @click="a = !a"
            >click</button>
            <div
                class="bg-blue-400 size-10"
                x-show="a"
                x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300"
                x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-x-20"
                x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-x-0"
            >
                content
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div
            x-data="{show:true}"
            x-show="show"
            x-init="setTimeout(() => show = false, 1000)"
            x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-1000"
            x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 transform"
            x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 transform"
            x-transition:leave="transition ease-in duration-1000"
            x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100 transform"
            x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0 transform"
            class="z-50 fixed inset-0 place-content-center grid bg-white h-screen"
        >
            <img
                src="https://dummyjson.com/icon/logo"
                alt=""
            >
        </div>
        <div class="place-items-center grid bg-green-300 h-screen"></div>
        <hr>
        <div x-data="{show:false}">
            <button @click="show=!show">toggle</button>
            <div
                class="bg-green-300 size-[3000px]"
                x-show="show"
                x-transition:enter.duration.1500ms.scale.0
                x-transition:leave.duration.1000ms.scale.0
            ></div>
        </div>
    </body>

</html>